Modified Time: None

Description: Friends of the Filipino People In Struggle (FFPS) called on March 6 to launch a global coordinated campaign to feature the National Democratic Front of the Philippines (N

Images: ['[ffps-friends-of-the-filipino-people-in-struggle-1024x577.png](https://philippinerevolution.nu/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/ffps-friends-of-the-filipino-people-in-struggle-1024x577.png)']

