# 8th of March in Finland

Author: lipunkantaja

Time: 2023-03-11T97:00:00-04:00

Images: ['[np23a.png](https://punalippu.noblogs.org/files/2023/03/np23a.png)', '[np23b.png](https://punalippu.noblogs.org/files/2023/03/np23b.png)', '[np23d.png](https://punalippu.noblogs.org/files/2023/03/np23d.png)', '[np23f.png](https://punalippu.noblogs.org/files/2023/03/np23f.png)', '[np23g.png](https://punalippu.noblogs.org/files/2023/03/np23g.png)', '[np23c.png](https://punalippu.noblogs.org/files/2023/03/np23c.png)', '[np23e.png](https://punalippu.noblogs.org/files/2023/03/np23e.png)', '[hki1.jpg](https://punalippu.noblogs.org/files/2023/03/hki1.jpg)', '[hki2.jpg](https://punalippu.noblogs.org/files/2023/03/hki2.jpg)']

Categories: ['Yleinen']

<!--METADATA-->

We publish English translations of two reports of activities in Finland.

**International Women 's Day 2023 in Tampere**

![](Images/PUNALIPPU/2023-03-11T97-00-00-04-00/np23a.png)Revolutionaries were again active on the occasion of international women's day in Tampere. Approaching the day, there were graffiti actions of which we also publish pictures that we received.![](Images/PUNALIPPU/2023-03-11T97-00-00-04-00/np23b.png)![](Images/PUNALIPPU/2023-03-11T97-00-00-04-00/np23d.png)![](Images/PUNALIPPU/2023-03-11T97-00-00-04-00/np23f.png)![](Images/PUNALIPPU/2023-03-11T97-00-00-04-00/np23g.png)Culmination was a broad demonstration that incorporated, among others, Russiananti-war activists. The demonstration, which was advertised with hundreds ofposters, demanded "more pay!", "down with the cost of living!", "againstpatriarchy!". Revolutionaries held high the banner and shout "forward towardsa revolutionary women's movement!", and spread [the](https://punalippu.noblogs.org/post/2023/03/01/kaduille-8-maaliskuuta/)[_joint_](https://punalippu.noblogs.org/post/2023/03/01/kaduille-8-maaliskuuta/)[declaration of Nordic revolutionarymovements](https://punalippu.noblogs.org/post/2023/03/01/kaduille-8-maaliskuuta/).Common slogans in the march included "down with the imperialist war and risingprices!", "down with misogyny!", "woman, life, freedom!", "for aninternational women's movement!", "wave upon wave, blow after blow, againstimperialism and patriarchy!", "end to the violence against women!".

![](Images/PUNALIPPU/2023-03-11T97-00-00-04-00/np23c.png)At the end of the demonstration there were speeches from the organizers, likeSolidarity with Women of Iran, Marxist Study Circle of Tampere and theCommunist Youth, and there was also a salutation from the rank-and-file of thetrade-union movement.

![](Images/PUNALIPPU/2023-03-11T97-00-00-04-00/np23e.png)**Helsinki: Women 's Day Demonstration**

![](Images/PUNALIPPU/2023-03-11T97-00-00-04-00/hki1.jpg)

"Party politics" was prohibited from the event, so the speeches could notrefer to the parliamentary elections that will take place in less than onemonth. However, among the speakers, there were electoral candidates, and alsothe Green Alliance had an electoral pop-up at the starting point of thedemonstration.

A small Marxist contingent participated in the demonstration with a banner"Down with imperialism!Down with patriarchy!Proletarian feminism forCommunism!" and a placat "¡Honor y gloria a la camarada Norah!". It was alsoreported that the joint declaration of the Anti-imperialist League(Finland),Anti-imperialist Collective(Denmark)and Struggle Committee(Norway)wasdistributed as a leaflet and was received positively by the masses.

![](Images/PUNALIPPU/2023-03-11T97-00-00-04-00/hki2.jpg)

News Source: [https://punalippu.noblogs.org/post/2023/03/11/8th-of-march-in-finland/](https://punalippu.noblogs.org/post/2023/03/11/8th-of-march-in-finland/)

